name: INCREMENTAL
text: Incremental wantlist entry, modifies existing wantlist for a peer or starts a new one if it was empty.

name: FULL
text: Full wantlist. This replaces the current wantlist for a peer.

name: SYNTHETIC
text: Synthetic entries derived from connection events. These are not part of the Bitswap protocol and are inserted by ipfs-json-to-csv.
